            <div
                class="p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center group md:lg:xl:border-r md:lg:xl:border-b hover:bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer">
                <span >
                <Image src={airport} class="p-2 rounded-full bg-black-500 text-white shadow-lg shadow-black-200" alt="Orlando Transportations Service" style={{objectFit: "contain"}}>
                </span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-700 mt-3">Airport Transportation</h3>
                <p class="mt-2">We provide a luxurious fleet, where comfort meets elegance, setting the stage for a journey that's not just secure but also a delightful experience. Whether it's the convenience of our MCO to Port Canaveral transfers, seamless transportation to Orlando Airport, or the personalized touch of our chauffeur services and black car services – each service is designed to bring a unique touch to your travel experience, ensuring a memorable and enjoyable journey with us.
</p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="p-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center group md:lg:xl:border-r md:lg:xl:border-b hover:bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer">
                <span >
                <Image src={disney} class="p-2 rounded-full bg-black-500 text-white shadow-lg shadow-black-200" alt="Orlando Transportations Service" style={{objectFit: "contain"}}>
                </span>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-700 mt-3"> Disney Transportation </h3>
                <p class="mt-2">We offer a trustworthy and comfortable Disney World transportation service tailored to pick you up from your chosen location and seamlessly drop you off at Disney World and the nearby resorts. Whether you're planning a family vacation or embarking on a tourism adventure, let us be your preferred choice for ensuring a secure and enjoyable journey as you explore the magic of the iconic theme parks and the diverse tourist attractions Orlando has to offer, including the renowned Walt Disney World Resort.
</p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center group   md:lg:xl:border-b hover:bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer">
                <span >
                <Image src={universal} class="p-2 rounded-full bg-black-500 text-white shadow-lg shadow-black-200" alt="Orlando Transportations Service" style={{objectFit: "contain"}}>
                </span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-700 mt-3">Universal Studios Transportation </h3>
                <p class="mt-2">We assure dependable and comfortable ground transportation services from your chosen location to Universal Studios and the adjacent theme parks and resorts. Whether you're planning a family vacation or embarking on a tourism adventure to discover all that Orlando has to offer, let us be your top choice as you explore the wonders of Universal Orlando Resort. 
</p>
            </div>


            <div class="p-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center group   md:lg:xl:border-r hover:bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer">
               <span >
                <Image src={excutive} class="p-2 rounded-full bg-black-500 text-white shadow-lg shadow-black-200" alt="Orlando Transportations Service" style={{objectFit: "contain"}}>
                </span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-700 mt-3"> Executive Transportation  
</h3>
                <p class="mt-2">Experience the epitome of VIP transportation with our private car service and executive car service for corporate travels in Orlando. Our commitment extends beyond efficiency to create a seamless and comfortable transportation experience, ensuring you not only reach your destination promptly but also in the epitome of style. Whether it's our chauffeured services for corporate events, facilitating business travelers, or delivering luxury black car service for a touch of sophistication  - each detail is tailored to redefine your expectations of premium transportation.
</p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center group    md:lg:xl:border-r hover:bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer">
                 <span >
                <Image src={wedding} class="p-2 rounded-full bg-black-500 text-white shadow-lg shadow-black-200" alt="Orlando Transportations Service" style={{objectFit: "contain"}}>
                </span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-700 mt-3">Wedding Limo </h3>
                <p class="mt-2">We specialize in offering luxury limousine services tailored for your wedding day. Immerse yourself in the luxury and charm of our wedding limo, providing an unforgettable experience for your special day. Our expert chauffeurs are dedicated to ensuring you're picked up with style and comfort, infusing an extra touch of elegance into every moment. With our private limo service, your wedding day becomes a seamless and enchanting celebration, leaving you with cherished memories that last a lifetime.
</p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center group     hover:bg-slate-50 cursor-pointer">
                <span >
                <Image src={cruise} class="p-2 rounded-full bg-black-500 text-white shadow-lg shadow-black-200" alt="Orlando Transportations Service" style={{objectFit: "contain"}}>
                </span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-700 mt-3">Cruise Transportation 
</h3>
                <p class="mt-2">Our luxury transportation services seamlessly connect you to and from Orlando to Port Canaveral, ensuring your cruise experience begins with a touch of elegance. With our ground transportation services, you can expect nothing short of excellence – from the moment you step into our fleet to the personalized care of our chauffeured services. Your journey with us is not just a transfer; it's a seamless and luxurious prelude to an unforgettable cruise adventure.
</p>
            </div>




